	   <tr><td colspan=2>1. Spirit Tap (HP heal)<br>2. Shock of Poison (DD, more mana efficient)<br>3. Darkness<br>4. VoS<br>5. Pet Attack with group, otherwise Fear solo.<br>6. Feign Death, or Shadowstep (useful in OOT)<br><br>for a 35ish + necro<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
